With former partner [[Christopher Knierim]], she is the 2009 [[United States Figure Skating Championships|U.S. junior silver medalist]]. They announced the end of their partnership on April 9, 2009. They had been coached by [[Dalilah Sappenfield]]. Carman then teamed up with [[A. J. Reiss]], with [[Peter Oppegard]] as coach. ==Competitive highlights== (with Reiss) {| class="wikitable" |- !
